## üöÄ How to Run Locally

> Note: Dialogflow CX runs on Google Cloud ‚Äì there's no "local" deployment, but here‚Äôs how you can explore it:

1. Go to [Dialogflow CX Console](https://dialogflow.cloud.google.com/cx)
2. Create a new Agent (or import provided agent ZIP)
3. Define intents like `mood_detect`, `media_type_choice`, `music_recommendation`, etc.
4. Use conditions to handle different moods and route responses accordingly
5. Add fulfillment responses or webhook for real-time recommendations

